; Regression test for issue #1634: Metadata/Note contents can't include a ledger formatted date (BZ#562)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1634
;
; Bug: When using typed metadata (Key:: Value), date-formatted values like 2024/03/15
; are parsed as arithmetic expressions (2024 / 3 / 15 = 44.977...) instead of as dates.
; Single-colon metadata (Key: Value) correctly preserves the date as a string.

2024/01/01 Payee
    ; Due:: 2024/03/15
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --limit 'account =~ /Food/' --format '%(tag("Due"))\n'
44.977777777778
end test
